{"tid":2305532,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"長州官立中學","createTime":"2020-11-29T16:46:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-30T07:02:34.000Z","uid":18012,"like":8,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"3312d2e966215a24f1ab293a9600d4e67334d2a1","tid":2305532,"uid":18012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T16:46:48.000Z","msg":"好似係天涯海角返學咁, 感覺好神奇<br />\n平時返學似渡假?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n多唔多人入到大學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n到底全校有幾多人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢幾間又係好想知, 全部都係天涯海角<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n佛教慧因法師紀念中學 @長洲大興堤路25號<br />\n南丫北段公立小學  @南丫島榕樹嶺1號<br />\n聖家學校 @坪洲聖家路1號<br />\n西貢中心李少欽紀念學校 @西貢惠民路號18號<br />\n西貢崇真天主教學校中學部 @西貢普通道A-E座<br />\n鄭植之中學 @西貢竹角路8號<br />\n佛教筏可紀念中學 @大澳大澳道99號<br />\n杯澳公立學校 @大嶼山貝澳羅屋村2<br />\n大嶼山國際學校 @DD 328 Tong Fuk Village Tong Fuk, Lantau Island<br />\n香港航海學校 @13-15, Tung Tau Wan Rd, Stanley"},{"pid":"552c9d3b4dd7eb4bba586285196e91c77e2d972e","tid":2305532,"uid":127511,"like":31,"dislike":3,"score":28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T16:47:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/197zDw5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F197zDw5.png&h=2c947fe0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n你噏乜柒呀石頭佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"490708864b3eaa951b25dcb27b